<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In a multi index search, id are change with :</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code> 
if ($indexShift != 0) {
      foreach ($hits as $hit) {
            $hit-&gt;id += $indexShift;
      }
}</code></pre>

<p>but id must be document id, so when i use</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
foreach($hits as $hit) {
        $document = $hit-&gt;getDocument();
}
</code></pre>

<p>there are an error.</p>

<p>So, to fix that, i have submitted a PR with update unit test to cover this case.
In Query\Hit, id is a unique hit (no based on id document) and document_id is the doc id.
So, no confusion and multi search run good.</p>

